data.description: If a spacious farmhouse is what you've been looking for, look no further! This well maintained 4, possibly 5 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home is waiting for your personal touch. Walk in to find a beautifully updated kitchen, opening to the large formal dining. Additional room off of the dining area can be used as an in home office or craft room. Cozy up to the wood burning stove in the spacious livingroom and enjoy the hardwood floors throughout. The back yard has a serene view, overlooking an apple orchard. There are multiple raised garden beds and fruit trees and a large parking area. 4yr gas furnace and new gas hot water heater. Beautiful property, don't wait to come and see it for yourself!
